text: Murat Pasha Mosque or Murad Pasha Mosque is the name of some Ottoman mosques. It may refer to: * Murat Pasha Mosque, Antalya, (built 1570) in Antalya, Turkey * Murad Pasha Mosque, Damascus, (built 1568) in Damascus, Syria * Murat Pasha Mosque, Aksaray, Istanbul tr:Murat Paşa Camii
title: Murat Pasha Mosque
